gedit: a lightweight text editor for the GNOME desktop
gedit:
gedit: gedit is a lightweight text editor for the GNOME desktop found in
gedit: many distributions of Linux, BSD and other Unix systems. Designed
gedit: for the X Window System, it uses the GTK+ and GNOME libraries. gedit
gedit: is released under the GNU General Public License (GPL).
gedit: 
gedit: gedit supports most standard editing features, and has a powerful
gedit: plugin system for adding even more.
